\n<br />\n之後入番籠全程縮埋一角，過幾日先正常番"},{"pid":"c4f7c2177c0e70591e6f72403864f91a6ca4b14b","tid":273342,"uid":54597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T15:12:00.000Z","msg":"以前養過<br />\n得七八年命 死左好傷心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"431c5ec2dfb04d310e0be8962fa04db8821a5a00","tid":273342,"uid":60500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T15:25:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以前養過<br />\n得七八年命 死左好傷心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n鼠類黎講七八年已經算長<br />\n倉鼠得兩三年命<br />\n不過愛寵物既人梗係想佢地長命百歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e84c7e36deeab816b0a177f6787c89ecc95c347","tid":273342,"uid":117628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T15:33:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>難唔難養？點餵</blockquote><br />\n依個見人見智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n長期要有草+早晚乾糧+一份菜</blockquote><br />\n仲要有C餅</blockquote><br />\n好難服侍，不了</blockquote><br />\n呢位巴打好直接<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係好事黎，起碼唔會害左隻寵物"},{"pid":"d4d79fa118c1f3b047118b22265ffbb4de216ff7","tid":273342,"uid":60500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T15:42:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以前養過，後來因工作問題送左去南丫島香草原<br />\n佢地堅係好細膽，有次俾佢走甩左，捉番佢果陣狂叫，個心跳得勁快，我幾驚個心會跳到爆開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後入番籠全程縮埋一角，過幾日先正常番</blockquote><br />\n心跳到爆開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9779654723f78502927b2e3a91c45eb34b3f11f","tid":273342,"uid":35749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T15:49:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><bloc